main event: A commercial aircraft observed what looked like a satellite moving from North to South for 5-6 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting was reported on 9-20-63., The object was described as looking like a star and the size of a sighting cloud., The observation was made by Slick 604, a commercial aircraft., The data collected suggested that the object was not a UFO but rather a satellite., The report included communications forwarded to various military and intelligence agencies.
